Cp%3EI've%20been%20watching%20what%20she%20wears%20when%20it's%20not%20my%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20dresses%20and%20jackets%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she's%20not%20afraid%20of%20color.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20think%20of%20this%20emerald%20green%20with%20gold%20buttons%20instead%20of%20a%20green%20button%20or%20black%3F%26quot%3B%20She%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20my%20god%2C%20I%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%20So%20we%20worked%20very%20well%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karoline%20Leavitt%20wears%20a%20green%20suit%20by%20Chris%20Cuozzo%20in%20the%20White%20House%20briefing%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681288fea466d2b74ab4a724%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22559%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaroline%20Leavitt%20wore%20an%20emerald-green%20suit%20featuring%20gold%20buttons%20designed%20by%20Christopher%20Cuozzo.%3Cp%3EMANDEL%20NGAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20does%20it%20take%20you%20to%20make%20these%20suits%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20a%20suit%20or%20really%20any%20garment%20takes%20about%20four%20to%20six%20weeks.%20Now%2C%20there's%20all%20these%20things%20that%20go%20into%20it%20that%20could%20add%20a%20longer%20time.%20We%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20custom%20linings%20where%20we%20print%20the%20photos%20onto%20silk%2C%20and%20then%20that%20lining%20goes%20inside%20the%20suit%2C%20and%20that's%20going%20to%20add%20approximately%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20you've%20been%20designing%20these%20suits%20for%20Karoline%2C%20have%20you%20put%20in%20any%20of%20these%20hidden%20details%20or%20custom%20linings%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20I'm%20going%20off%20memory%20here%2C%20but%20I'm%20pretty%20confident%20we%20did%20an%20American%20flag%20lining%20in%20one%20of%20her%20suits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20always%20visible%20when%20you're%20just%20looking%20at%20photos%20from%20press%20conferences.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know.%20I've%20got%20to%20get%20her%20to%20flash%20that%20jacket%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karoline%20Leavitt%20wears%20a%20navy%20pinstripe%20suit%20by%20Christopher%20Cuozzo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681293b33fe8d3928364914c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaroline%20Leavitt%20in%20a%20navy%20pinstripe%20suit%20by%20Christopher%20Cuozzo.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Howard%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20mentioned%20that%20there's%20a%20lot%20to%20consider%20when%20you're%20designing%20suits%20for%20people%20based%20on%20their%20profession.%20What%20sort%20of%20considerations%20do%20you%20have%20when%20you're%20designing%20suits%20for%20someone%20like%20Karoline%2C%20who%20is%20in%20such%20a%20public%20and%20high-pressure%20role%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVery%20good%20question.%20Classic%20reigns%20supreme%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20want%20anything%20trendy.%20She's%20a%20very%20classy%20woman%2C%20but%20she's%20down-to-business%2C%20for%20sure.%20I%20don't%20envision%20her%20wanting%20to%20do%20some%20very%20loud%20plaid%20suit%20that's%20a%20bunch%20of%20different%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20get%20to%20know%20her%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20and%20watch%20her%20and%20see%20what%20she%20does%2C%20I%20think%20the%20classics%20will%20usually%20win%2C%20with%20a%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20chose%20red%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised.%20It's%20my%20company%20color.%20It's%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20colors.%20It%20screams%20confidence.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20yeah.%20This%20will%20be%20awesome.%26quot%3B%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20that's%20the%20one%20we%20did%20the%20American%20flag%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20on%20the%20younger%20sid