he%20gift%20is%20raising%20red%20flags%20for%20legal%20experts.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20walks%20off%20Air%20Force%20One%20.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6821981cc6ad288d14809e76%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20walks%20off%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20the%20official%20presidential%20plane.%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20expected%20to%20receive%20a%20luxury%20jet%20from%20Qatar%20for%20use%20as%20the%20new%20Air%20Force%20One.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20gift%20raises%20questions%20under%20the%20foreign%20emoluments%20clause%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BA%20gift%20of%20this%20size%20from%20a%20foreign%20government%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20our%20nation's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jessica%20Levison%2C%20a%20law%20professor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EReports%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20is%20expected%20to%20receive%20a%20luxury%20jet%20as%20a%20gift%20from%20the%20Qatari%20royal%20family%20have%20drawn%20questions%20and%20criticism%20from%20legal%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20the%20concern%20is%20the%20foreign%20emoluments%20clause%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20prevents%20a%20person%20in%20a%20government%20office%20from%20accepting%20gifts%20or%20benefits%20from%20foreign%20parties%20without%20congressional%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20definitely%20violates%20the%20foreign%20emoluments%20clause%20unless%20Congress%20gives%20consent%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Painter%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20White%20House%20ethics%20lawyer%20in%20the%20George%20W.%20Bush%20administration%20and%20a%20professor%20of%20corporate%20law%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20the%20plane%20goes%20to%20his%20presidential%20library%20after%20four%20years%20does%20not%20change%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gift%20from%20Qatar%2C%20a%20Boeing%20747-8%20jumbo%20jet%2C%20will%20be%20used%20as%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-one-features%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20Force%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F05%2F11%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-qatar-jet-gift-air-force-one.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump%2Ftrump-administration-will-accept-luxury-jet-qatar-use-air-force-one-rcna206111%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutlets%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Sunday%2C%20citing%20anonymous%20sources.%20It%20will%20be%20donated%20to%20Trump's%20presidential%20library%20when%20he%20leaves%20office.%20A%20new%20747-8%20costs%20about%20%24400%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20appeared%20to%20confirm%20the%20reports%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Defense%20Department%20is%20getting%20a%20GIFT%2C%20FREE%20OF%20CHARGE%2C%20of%20a%20747%20aircraft%20to%20replace%20the%2040%20year%20old%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20temporarily%2C%20in%20a%20very%20public%20and%20transparent%20transaction%2C%20so%20bothers%20the%20Crooked%20Democrats%20that%20they%20insist%20we%20pay%2C%20TOP%20DOLLAR%2C%20for%20the%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAli%20Al-Ansari%2C%20Qatar's%20media%20attach%C3%A9%20to%20the%20US%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20transfer%20of%20an%20aircraft%20for%20temporary%20use%20as%20Air%20Force%20One%20is%20%26quot%3Bcurrently%20under%20consideration.%26quot%3B%20The%20matter%20%26quot%3Bremains%20under%20review%20by%20the%20respective%20legal%20departments%2C%20and%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Al-Ansari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c8995dc-d7a4-4553-a2c9-a7150beb62bb%5C%22%3EAn%20'unprecedented'%20gift%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20arrives%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%20on%20October%2028%2C%202020%20in%20Bullhead%20City%2C%20Arizona.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c86bec69253ccddf98534a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20building%20of%20a%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20delays.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20Brekken%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJessica%20Levinson%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20and%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Public%20Service%20Institute%20at%20Loyola%20Law%20School%2C%20said%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20foreign%20emoluments%20clause%2C%20federal%20statutes%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Foreign%20Gifts%20and%20Decorations%20Act%20and%20anti-bribery%20laws%2C%20may%20come%20into%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOutside%20of%20the%20legal%20context%2C%20it%20is%20fair%20to%20ask%20whether%20the%20acceptance%20of%20this%20gift%20could%20give%20rise%20to%20an%20apparent%20conflict%20of%20interest%20or%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaroline%20Leavitt%2C%20the%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20any%20gift%20from%20a%20foreign%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Balways%20accepted%20in%20full%20compliance%20with%20all%20applicable%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevinson%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20size%20of%20the%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20remember%20is%20that%20the%20acceptance%20of%20a%20gift%20of%20this%20size%20from%20a%20foreign%20government%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20our%20nation's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Levinson%20added.%20%26quot%3BHence%20we%20do%20not%20have%20any%20direct%20historical%20analogs%20for%20this%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20legal%20mechanisms%20for%20addressing%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20foreign%20emoluments%20clause%2C%20Painter%20pointed%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestigation%20and%20possible%20impeachment%20is%20one%20remedy%2C%20but%20that's%20up%20to%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20Painter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22034e37ef-49ce-43ec-b75c-7e0ab44075d6%5C%22%3EUS%20politicians%20react%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senate%20Minority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677ebd3ef83fcec7e5b51171%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221319%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESenate%20Minority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20was%20among%20the%20Democratic%20politicians%20to%20criticize%20the%20gift.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20drew%20criticism%20online%20from%20some%20leading%20US%20Democrats%20and%20at%20least%20one%20far-right%20activist%20with%20close%20ties%20to%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20says%20'America%20First'%20like%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20brought%20to%20you%20by%20Qatar.%20It's%20not%20just%20bribery%2C%20it's%20premium%20foreign%20influence%20with%20extra%20legroom%2C%26quot%3B%20Senate%20minority%20leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20wrote%20on%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Rep.%20Adam%20Schiff%20quoted%20part%20of%20the%20foreign%20emoluments%20clause%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BSeems%20pretty%20clear%20that%20a%20%24400%20million%20'air%20palace'%20from%20a%20foreign%20emir%20qualifies.%20The%20corruption%20is%20brazen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Rep.%20Jamie%20Raskin%20also%20took%20to%20X%20to%20criticize%20the%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20must%20seek%20Congress'%20consent%20to%20take%20this%20%24300%20million%20gift%20from%20Qatar.%20The%20Constitution%20is%20perfectly%20clear%3A%20no%20present%20'of%20any%20kind%20whatever'%20from%20a%20foreign%20state%20without%20Congressional%20permission.%20A%20gift%20you%20use%20for%20four%20years%20and%20then%20deposit%20in%20your%20library%20is%20still%20a%20gift%20(and%20a%20grift)%2C%26quot%3B%20Raskin%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaura%20Loomer%2C%20a%20far-right%20activist%20with%20direct%20ties%20to%20Trump%2C%20also%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20criticize%20news%20of%20the%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20going%20to%20be%20such%20a%20stain%20on%20the%20admin%20if%20this%20is%20true.%20And%20I%20say%20that%20as%20someone%20who%20would%20take%20a%20bullet%20for%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Loomer%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20putting%20pressure%20on%20Boeing%20to%20deliver%20the%20next%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-one-new-planes-trump-boeing-delivery-delays-president-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebehind%20schedule%20and%20over%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20was%20first%20tapped%20in%202015%20to%20deliver%20the%20two%20new%20presidential%20planes.%20The%20delivery%20was%20initially%20set%20for%202024%2C%20then%20delayed%20until%202027%20or%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20US%20Air%20Force%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-one-new-planes-trump-boeing-delivery-delays-president-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Boeing%20could%20deliver%20the%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20jets%20by%202027%2C%20while%20Trump%20is%20still%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b