y%20demands%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20study%2C%20she%20added%20%E2%80%94%20she%20often%20uses%20Sundays%20for%20catching%20up%2C%20learning%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bplay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSunday%20morning%2C%20it's%20a%20full%20workday%20for%20me%2C%20and%20it's%20%3Cem%3Emy%3C%2Fem%3E%20workday%2C%26quot%3B%20Rangan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20time%20I%20read%2C%20this%20is%20the%20time%20I%20do%20deep%20thinking%2C%20this%20is%20the%20time%20I%20write.%20It's%20a%20full%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERangan%20has%20set%20a%20hard%20line%2C%20though.%20Whenever%20she's%20finally%20done%20with%20work%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20she's%20firmly%20clocking%20out%20for%20her%20version%20of%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20what%20I%20try%20to%20do%20is%2C%20Friday%20night%20whenever%20I'm%20done%20%E2%80%94%20it%20might%20be%208%2C%209%2C%2010%20%E2%80%94%20whatever%20time%20I'm%20done%20on%20Friday%2C%20I%20don't%20touch%20my%20computer%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20about%20work%20'til%20Sunday%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20Rangan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20boundaries%20came%20about%2C%20in%20part%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20blurring%20of%20the%20home%20and%20the%20workplace%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20Because%20there%20was%20no%20real%20distinction%20between%20her%20office%20and%20what%20had%20previously%20been%20places%20of%20rest%2C%20Rangan%20said%20she%20had%20to%20set%20mental%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20found%2C%20especially%20post-COVID%20or%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20is%20that%20there%20was%20no%20constraint%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYour%20office%20was%20two%20minutes%20away%20from%20your%20kitchen%2C%20and%20so%20you're%20working%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20that%20when%20she%20does%20pause%20on%20Saturdays%2C%20she%20doesn't%20send%20out%20so%20much%20as%20an%20email%2C%20even%20if%20a%20board%20member%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20