%20were%20invited%20to%20visit%20the%20firm's%20headquarters.%20The%20club%20leader%20is%20one%20of%20many%20students%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20to%20protect%20their%20future%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20so%20many%20opportunities%20to%20network%20internally%20and%20have%20specific%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20drop%20links%20that%20these%20recruiters%20give%20to%20the%20club%20specifically%2C%20that%20are%20only%20open%20to%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%20about%20his%20campus%20club%20experience.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20book.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hedge%20fund%20Balyasny%20went%20to%20campus%20clubs%20to%20find%20candidates%20for%20its%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbalyasny-careers-stock-pitch-competition-internship-campus-recruiting-schools-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20pitch%20competitions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20uses%20to%20identify%20talent.%20A%20private%20equity%20worker%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BNo.%201%20thing%26quot%3B%20she%20looked%20for%20when%20she%20was%20a%20recruiting%20captain%20of%20an%20investment%20bank%20was%20whether%20students%20from%20her%20alma%20mater%20had%20been%20members%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20two%20most%20prestigious%20investment%20clubs%20on%20campus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Wharton%20School%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e5d3c9efee23d29f2062c39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Wharton%20School.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Mostoller%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECompetition%20to%20get%20into%20campus%20clubs%20has%20gotten%20so%20intense%20that%20Georgetown's%20McDonough%20School%20of%20Business%20barred%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgeorgetownvoice.com%2F2025%2F04%2F12%2Finclusivity-or-inefficiency-msabs-open-access-policy-still-sparks-debate-two-years-later%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst-semester%20freshmen%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20joining%20them%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20have%20balked%20at%20the%20rule%2C%20saying%20it%20puts%20them%20behind%20in%20recruiting%20for%20Wall%20Street%20internships%2C%20which%20students%20must%20apply%20for%20halfway%20through%20their%20sophomore%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKids%20are%20just%20so%20much%20less%20prepared%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20student%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgeorgetownvoice.com%2F2025%2F04%2F12%2Finclusivity-or-inefficiency-msabs-open-access-policy-still-sparks-debate-two-years-later%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeorgetown%20Voice%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20impact%20the%20rule%20was%20having%20on%20students%20interested%20in%20working%20on%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20publication%20reported%20that%20the%20rule%20wasn't%20making%20the%20admissions%20process%20any%20less%20competitive%20and%20was%20just%20delaying%20the%20flood%20of%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20pressure%20these%20young%20people%20face%20may%20feel%20exaggerated%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20signs%20that%20the%20stakes%20are%20all%20too%20real.%20Wall%20Street%20firms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-internship-just-got-harder-summer-analyst-acceptance-rate-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20disclosed%20record%20levels%20of%20applicants%20to%20their%20internship%20programs.%20And%20Wall%20Street's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestment-banking-summer-internship-recruiting-more-competitive-tips-students-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearlier-than-ever%20%3C%2Fa%3Erecruiting%20schedule%20compelled%20Steve%20Sibley%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Indiana%20University's%20Kelley%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20to%20move%20an%20introductory%20corporate%20finance%20class%20he%20runs%20from%20the%20fall%20of%20students'%20sophomore%20year%20to%20the%20spring%20of%20their%20freshman%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20we%20weren't%20offering%20classes%20early%20enough%20for%20these%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Campus%20of%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e2d13a466d2b74ab5880f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223374%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20campus%20of%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%3Cp%3ERobert%20Knopes%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20result%20has%20been%20a%20club%20culture%20that%20often%20mimics%20the%20industry%20itself%2C%20including%20a%20cutthroat%20selection%20process.%20Some%20clubs%20conduct%20three%20to%20five%20rounds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-tips-to-summer-analyst-internship-at-investment-bank-lazard-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterviews%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20students%20told%20BI%2C%20which%20can%20involve%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20review%20(yes%2C%20your%20high%20school%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9)%2C%20a%20social%20assessment%2C%20and%20multiple%20technical%20rounds%20in%20which%20you'll%20be%20grilled%20on%20real-world%20finance%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20club%20leader%20described%20a%20freshman%20applicant%20who%20froze%20and%20started%20crying%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-a-goldman-sachs-internship-summer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflubbing%20a%20question%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20watch%2C%20and%2C%20needless%20to%20say%2C%20the%20student%20didn't%20make%20it%20to%20the%20next%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20it%20sucks%20when%20you%20have%20to%20reject%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20club%20leader%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20have%20X%20amount%20of%20applicants%20and%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20spots.%20And%20that%20is%20literally%20just%20how%20the%20industry%20is%20set%20up%20as%20well.%20It's%20hypercompetitive%2C%20it's%20overwhelming%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20be%20pushing%20constantly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20students%20BI%20spoke%20with%20echoed%20that%20low%20acceptance%20rates%20were%20extreme%20and%20sometimes%20ridiculous.%20They%20also%20said%20it's%20this%20way%20for%20a%20reason%2C%20including%20the%20difficulty%20of%20managing%20and%20teaching%20hundreds%20of%20other%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20only%20have%20so%20much%20bandwidth%20as%20people%20running%20the%20club%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Wharton%20junior%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20is%20lower%20if%20you're%20dealing%20with%20300.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20for%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20being%20a%20sought-after%20club%20brings%20a%20level%20of%20prestige%20and%20bragging%20rights%20for%20those%20who%20manage%20to%20get%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20be%20in%20the%20club%20where%20so%20many%20people%20want%20to%20get%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20club%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20freshman%20at%20%3Ca%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-day-in-the-life-senior-georgetown-university-college-2023-5%5C%22%3EGeorgetown%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202022%2C%20Jonathan%20Rothschild%20refused%20to%20apply%20to%20finance%20clubs%20his%20first%20semester%2C%20he%20said%2C%20once%20he%20learned%20about%20the%20rigorous%20interview%20processes%20and%20acceptance%20rates%20of%20under%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20look%2C%20I%20just%20got%20here.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20if%20I%20want%20to%20be%20in%20this%20club%2C%20let%20a