0see%20are%20due%20to%20drowning%20in%20trawl%20nets.%20The%20problem%20isn%E2%80%99t%20visible%20to%20those%20ashore%20%E2%80%94%20it%20happens%20far%20from%20sight%2C%20in%20the%20deeper%20waters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrem%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20all%20fishermen%20are%20the%20same.%20Most%20of%20us%20want%20the%20sea%20to%20flourish.%20But%20deep-sea%20trawling%20without%20following%20appropriate%20guidelines%20is%20destructive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEcological%20wisdom%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reverence%20towards%20these%20Ridley%20turtles%20isn%E2%80%99t%20rooted%20in%20tradition%20alone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20ecological%20wisdom%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%20Olive%20Ridleys%20feed%20primarily%20on%20jellyfish%20and%20seaweed.%20Jellyfish%2C%20often%20seen%20as%20pests%20by%20fishermen%2C%20can%20damage%20nets%20and%20kill%20smaller%20fish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20turtles%20help%20maintain%20a%20balanced%20food%20chain.%20Where%20there%20are%20turtles%2C%20there%20is%20good%20water%20flow%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20more%20fish%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Prem.%20Turtles%20are%20thus%20indicators%20of%20a%20healthy%20marine%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20sustains%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20the%20very%20people%20often%20accused%20of%20harming%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20turtles%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20fishermen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Palayam%20says.%20%E2%80%9CKutty%20Amma%20brings%20the%20fish%20with%20her.%20When%20she%20comes%20to%20lay%20eggs%2C%20the%20tiny%20fish%20get%20stuck%20to%20her%20belly.%20This%20is%20how%20we%20survive