ability%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20B2B%20business%20serves%20clients%20like%20Wipro%2C%20JP%20Morgan%2C%20ICICI%20Prudential%2C%20and%20VMart%2C%20and%20they%20work%20directly%20with%20schools%20through%20distributors.%20On%20the%20B2C%20front%2C%20Rescript%E2%80%99s%20products%20are%20available%20in%20retail%20stores%20such%20as%20Sapna%20Book%20House%20and%20Crossword%2C%20and%20soon%20through%20Swiggy%20and%20Blinkit%20for%20quick%20commerce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuchi%20Rai%2C%20Head%20of%20Science%20at%20Sanskriti%20The%20Gurukul%20for%20over%208%20years%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20leading%20the%20Department%20of%20Environmental%20Science%20in%202016%20and%20have%20since%20worked%20to%20integrate%20sustainability%20into%20our%20curriculum%20from%20Classes%201%20to%2012.%20At%20Sanskriti%20The%20Gurukul%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20CISCE%20school%2C%20we%20approach%20every%20resource%20with%20conservation%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202096px)%20100vw%2C%202096px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%204%20recently%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443.jpg%202096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443-1200x675.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FRescript-Founders-at-Shark-Tank-1_11zon-1746712443-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426234%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%204%20recently%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20key%20projects%2C%20%E2%80%98Paper%20Out%20of%20Paper%E2%80%99%2C%20involves%20students%20recycling%20used%20notebooks%20into%20handmade%20sheets%2C%20a%20practical%20way%20to%20understand%20reuse%20and%20waste%20reduction.%20Discovering%20Rescript%20aligned%20with%20this%20effort%2C%20showing%20students%20how%20small%20actions%20can%20scale%20into%20impactful%20ideas%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20introduced%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293149%2Fbrothers-sustainable-startup-chatur-chidiyaa-products-give-jobs-to-ex-poacher-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrand%E2%80%99s%20notebooks%20across%20all%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20for%20teachers%E2%80%99%20planning.%20It%20is%20encouraging%20to%20see%20students%20engaging%20with%20sustainable%20choices%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20collaborations%20like%20this%20can%20nurture%20both%20awareness%20and%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98At%20Rescript%2C%20we%20are%20hands-on%2C%20intentional%2C%20and%20honest%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20all%20this%20is%20a%20team%20of%20just%20nine.%20In%20the%20early%20days%2C%20the%20co-founders%20handled%20everything%2C%20from%20packing%20orders%20to%20attending%20sales%20meetings.%20Their%20first%20hire%2C%20Pratik%20Dawda%2C%20was%20a%20law%20student%20who%20managed%20their%20social%20media%20(part-time).%20He%20now%20heads%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20entire%20digital%20and%20content%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20early%20on%20that%20social%20media%20would%20be%20our%20voice.%20It%20is%20how%20we%20educated%20our%20audience%2C%20gained%20trust%2C%20and%20scaled%20our%20message%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Rescript%20team%20comprises%20nine%20people%20who%20look%20after%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20stationery%20items%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-62_11zon-1746718152-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426292%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Rescript%20team%20comprises%20nine%20people%20who%20look%20after%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20stationery%20items%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratik%20Dawda%2C%20who%20has%20been%20with%20Rescript%20for%20over%203.5%20years%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20lead%20all%20our%20digital%20marketing%20efforts%2C%20including%20paid%20ads%2C%20content%2C%20brand%20partnerships%2C%20WhatsApp%20communications%2C%20and%20performance%20strategy.%20I%20also%20support%20B2B%20lead%20generation%20and%20collaborate%20closely%20with%20our%20web%2C%20product%2C%20and%20design%20teams%20to%20grow%20our%20online%20presence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Rescript%2C%20we%20are%20hands-on%2C%20intentional%2C%20and%20honest.%20We%20do%20not%20chase%20trends%2C%20instead%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20building%20trust%20around%20a%20genuinely%20better%20product.%20We%20aim%20to%20make%20people%20think%20differently%20about%20paper%20and%20to%20be%20memorable%20without%20being%20loud.%20Value-led%20storytelling%2C%20loyalty%2C%20and%20consistent%20engagement%20are%20central%20to%20everything%20we%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20the%20brand%20felt%20like%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%20It%20is%20hard%20not%20to%20believe%20in%20a%20product%20that%20just%20makes%20sense%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20world%20that%20needs%20better%20alternatives.%20Seeing%20people%20make%20the%20switch%20and%20knowing%20we%20are%20driving%20that%20momentum%20is%20what%20makes%20this%20journey%20so%20rewarding%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20social%20media%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20zero%20to%20crores%20without%20cutting%20a%20tree%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024-25%20financial%20year%2C%20Rescript%20recorded%20Rs%205%20crore%20in%20revenue%2C%20up%20from%20Rs%203.3%20crore%20the%20previous%20year%20and%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20the%20year%20before%20that.%20They%20completed%201%2C500%20B2B%20invoices%20and%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20D2C%20orders%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20pricing%20remains%20similar%20to%20conventional%20statione